  ABSTRACT = {
In this paper the results of a search for pairs of bilinear equations
of the type $A^i(D_x,D_t)F\cdot F+B^i(D_x,D_t)G\cdot F+
C^i(D_x,D_t)G\cdot G=O$, $i= 1,2$, which have standard type
