are auxiliary functions.  In this paper it is assumed that $B^1$ and
$B^2$ are even and proportional, and that $A^i$ and $C^i$ are
quadratic. As new results, $B^1=aD_x^3D_t+D_tD_y+b$, $A^2=-C^2=D_xD_t$
