  ABSTRACT = {
In this paper the results of a search for complex bilinear equations
with two-soliton solutions are presented.  The following basic types
are discussed: (a) the nonlinear Schr-dinger equation $B(D_x,\ldots
)G\cdot F=0$, $A(D_x,D_t)F\cdot F = GG^*$, and (b) the Benjamin-Ono
